title: 21 September
info:
There isn't really much to say about "21 September".
I wanted to do something different from the norm and to remove some dust from one of my hardware synths.
So, basically, i did an atmospheric electro-minimal track; most of the sounds come out from the Virus C synth and it was sequenced in Ableton Live; about 2 afternoons of work.
Hope you like it!
